am\": \"the follow-up message\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"your foot\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Well, I am actually fine, and despite what big media conspiracies would have you believe, I wasn't 'sent home' from the Olympics,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"what big media conspiracies\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"NBC simply looked at my foot, declared me legally a leper, and exiled me here, to the island of Malta!\\\"\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999392836446018, \"rank\": 5.696907342717682e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1357, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999230994428719, \"rank\": 7.141874249277763e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my foot\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"the island\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He joked that although Malta does not have \\\"many Olympians competing this year,\\\" it does have casinos where he could spend \\\"the hundreds of dollars I have earned as a surfing correspondent.\\\"\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"score\": 0.9999230994428719, \"rank\": 7.141874249277763e-05, \"text\": \"Malta\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malta\"}], \"noun_phrase