, \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The medical staff at this point, they know my name.\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2765}, {\"ngram\": \"my name\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are very familiar with my badge ID number, they know I am allergic to penicillin.\\\"\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my badge ID number\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"penicillin\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jost also shared that medical staff told him his \\\"infection has not improved,\\\" before he made a joke about his condition: \\\"Why did the chicken cross the road?\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 3033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jost\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"medical staff\", \"from\": 2897, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"infection\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2934}, {\"ngram\": \"a joke\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"his condition\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"the chicken\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To peck at the staph infection in my foot.\\\"\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the staph infection\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"my foot\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to his staph infection, Jost explained thathe also had an ear infectionand could not get his feet or head wet.\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3201, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3115, \"end\": 3119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Jost\", \"score\": 0.9997836894994293, \"rank\": 0.00019299881294512376, \"text\": \"Jost\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215